and needs assistance,
I'll do whatever I can,

6
00:00:17,467 --> 00:00:21,167
-if there's anything I can do.
-If it stays this way, Pandai might

7
00:00:21,233 --> 00:00:24,533
be merged into them. Right now,

8
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:26,433
we need huge
financial assistance.

9
00:00:26,500 --> 00:00:30,067
This is Chairman Oizumi and his
secretary, Yokoyama from Hokueisha.

10
00:00:30,133 --> 00:00:32,867
About finance, I'll be discussing
with you,

11
00:00:32,933 --> 00:00:34,400
instead of my father.

12
00:00:35,233 --> 00:00:38,100
Dad's condition is not that great.

13
00:00:38,167 --> 00:00:40,167
If I take over the company...

14
