15
00:00:53,667 --> 00:00:56,800
What an honor for us to receive
a visit

16
00:00:56,867 --> 00:01:00,567
-from you. Thank you so much.
-Not at all.

17
00:01:01,167 --> 00:01:04,100
I had some business to take care of
in this area also.

18
00:01:05,167 --> 00:01:06,633
Are you alone today?

19
00:01:08,300 --> 00:01:11,800
I wanted talk to you
in person today.

20
00:01:12,800 --> 00:01:13,867
To me?

21
00:01:16,333 --> 00:01:19,700
Naoki, would you like to have an
arranged marriage meeting?

22
00:01:26,233 --> 00:01:29,700
I'm hesitant to ask you while
Mr. Irie is hospitalized,

23
00:01:29,767 --> 00:01:31,900
but I have a granddaughter.

24
00:01:33,300 --> 00:01:37,533
She's the same age as you and goes
to University of the Sacred heart.

25
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:39,833
That's the most prestigious school.

26
00:01:41,433 --> 00:01:45,800
What do you think, Naoki?
How about seeing her once?

27
00:01:51,133 --> 00:01:54,533
You're young. I know you can't
give me an answer right away.

28
00:01:55,467 --> 00:02:00,133
Discuss with your parents and
give me an answer in a few days.

29
00:02:04,433 --> 00:02:07,567
We'll discuss about the investment
after that.

30
00:02:08,733 --> 00:02:12,867
-Sorry for the surprise visit.
-No problem at all.

31
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:19,767
Then Naoki, think about it
really well.

32
00:02:20,233 --> 00:02:22,667
Yes. Thank you.

33
00:02:31,833 --> 00:02:33,033
Naoki.

34
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:38,500
This will be a good deal...

35
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:40,867
for the company also, right?

36
00:02:44,633 --> 00:02:48,900
-What do you mean, Naoki?
-Honey, calm down.

37
00:02:49,767 --> 00:02:51,067
However...

38
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:53,900
having a marriage meeting with

39
