the granddaughter of Chairman Oizumi?
What's going on?

40
00:02:59,100 --> 00:03:00,633
Nothing.

41
00:03:02,067 --> 00:03:06,367
Could it be that it's for
the financial assistance?

42
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:14,267
Since we came here without
telling them,

43
00:03:14,333 --> 00:03:17,333
-will Dad be surprised?
-What do we do?

44
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:20,667
-Will it be bad for his heart?
-What are you talking about?

45
00:03:20,733 --> 00:03:24,500
He'll get so much better to get rid
of the disease when he sees you.

46
00:03:27,067 --> 00:03:28,833
Don't underestimate
your parents.

47
00:03:31,267 --> 00:03:32,533
I...

48
00:03:33,633 --> 00:03:35,200
never wanted to sacrifice you...

49
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:38,100
to save the company.

50
00:03:38,167 --> 00:03:41,767
He's right. Marrying her is
out of the question.

51
00:03:41,833 --> 00:03:44,533
Marrying? My brother is?

52
00:03:46,167 --> 00:03:51,500
I'm proud of myself to make Pandai
big in one generation.

53
00:03:52,467 --> 00:03:54,567
So, don't be so considerate
for me.

54
00:03:56,500 --> 00:04:00,467
Marry a person you really love.

55
00:04:04,767 --> 00:04:05,933
I like her.

56
00:04:09,133 --> 00:04:14,133
When I saw her picture,
she was my type.

57
00:04:15,933 --> 00:04:17,300
Brother.

58
00:04:17,900 --> 00:04:19,933
-Are you serious?
-Yuki.

59
00:04:20,433 --> 00:04:23,367
Are you really marrying her?
Because....

60
00:04:23,433 --> 00:04:26,633
Kotoko! Mr. Aihara too.

61
00:04:38,067 --> 00:04:39,233
Irie.

62
00:04:40,233 --> 00:04:42,500
Is it true that you're having
a marriage meeting?

63
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,700
Yeah.

64
00:04:48,667 --> 00:04:50,000
This Sunday.

65
00:04:51,767 --> 00:04:53,533
Since my dad is like this,

66
00:04:54,167 --> 00:04:57,467
